snippet.title: Longplay of Contra: Legacy of War
snippet.description:
Longplay of Contra: Legacy of War, played as the NTSC version on the PlayStation. This game's version was released on Nov. 30th, 1996. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Start
0:00:25 - Intro Movie
0:01:39 - Stage 1: Urban Warfare
0:06:46 - Stage 2: Jungle Conflict

0:33:11 - Stage 5: Bad Wavelength
0:41:19 - Stage 6: Planet LP-426
0:47:44 - Ending + Credits
0:52:47 - Arcade Mini Game: Pac-Tank
1:10:50 - Arcade Mini Game: Star Shooter Game

By: Retro Game Spacko
